<h1>Autoslide with custom animations</h1>

{{#markdown}}
###HTML
```
<div id="demoSlider" class="mbslider">
  <div class="item"><img class="animated zoomIn zoomOut" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
  <div class="item"><img class="animated fadeInDown fadeOutUp" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
  <div class="item"><img class="animated rotateInBig rotateOutBig" class="animated zoomIn zoomOut" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
  <div class="item"><img class="animated bounceIn bounceOut" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
  <div class="item"><img class="animated bounceInRight bounceOutLeft" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
  <div class="item"><img class="animated flipInY flipOutY" src="https://unsplash.it/1280/720?random&p={{random 1000000000 10000000000}}"></div>
</div>
```
###Javascript
```
<script>
  $(document).ready(function($){
    var slider = $('#demoSlider').mbSlider({
      auto: true,
      autoControls: true,
      customAnimation: "slide",
      pauseBeforeOut:1500
    });
  });

</script>
```
